title: SKILLET SAUSAGE AND POTATOES RECIPE
directions: Heat up a skillet over medium heat. Add the potatoes and carrots, cook for 5 minutes, turning the potatoes and carrots over occasionally. Add the red onion, stir to combine well with the potatoes and carrots. Add the sausages and cook for 1-2 minutes. Top with some shredded cheddar cheese (if using), serve immediately.
ingredients: 1 pack Johnsonville Smoked Sausage and Cheddar Cheese, cut into short strips
